<p>Hmm. Now, <code>$paymentToken</code> might be blank. But Stripe will be <em>really</em> angry if we
try to attach an empty <em>source</em> to the Customer. Instead of doing this all at once,
add a new <code>$data</code> array variable, and move the <code>email</code> key into it. Then, pass
<code>$data</code> to the <code>create()</code> call:</p>
