<p>Oh yea - this method looks at the <code>sources</code> key on the Customer to get the card brand
and last four digits. In our app, every Customer has exactly <em>one</em> card, so we use the <code>0</code>
key. But guess what! Not anymore: a customer <em>might</em> have zero cards.</p>
<p>So we just need to code defensively: add an if statement: if <code>!$stripeCustomer-&gt;sources-&gt;data</code>,
just return: there's no card details to update:</p>
